{"tid":1557031,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"大家的簽名有用! 逾百英國議員籲英聯邦國家給香港居民第二公民身份","createTime":"2019-09-10T03:15:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-10T03:15:38.000Z","uid":293722,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"9f6ba5b29db19798b481e6dc8510474c994a2b00","tid":1557031,"uid":293722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T03:15:38.000Z","msg":"近130名英國國會議員，包括前港督彭定康，向外相藍韜文發表聯署信，呼籲英聯邦國家給予香港居民第二公民身份及居留權。<br />\n<br />\n聯署信說，中國最近的言論及行動，表明北京領導層已經脫離基本法規定，對維護香港生活方式的承諾，英聯邦國家應該為香港人提供保障，又要求將有關討論，列入明年在盧旺達舉行的英聯邦政府領導人會議議程。<br />\n<br />\n目前很多香港居民都持有BNO護照，但不享有英國居留權，藍韜文日前表明，若果更改規定，可能會破壞一國兩制。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1479727-20190910.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1479727-20190910.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=SMAvs7Hy8J1z03%2F%2B44sdD2lERb1kSGFVDbesiz0gOXg%3D&h=04c4e5d3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1479727-20190910.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=2d4fc25e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1479727-20190910.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"}]}